{"tid":554540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得有啲咩係人生一定要做","createTime":"2018-02-08T15:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T13:19:35.000Z","uid":97958,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6733a32df5dcedce211d990243b796c706886736","tid":554540,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:21:59.000Z","msg":"啱啱同呀爸呀媽傾計，佢哋覺得人要結婚，結完婚要生仔<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得最緊要開心同簡單就夠，如果覺得自己一個好開心既點解要結婚，冇能力又唔點中意小朋友既點解要生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eae7fcd35c4ea44b8a4bbe2dd86d32127df3090","tid":554540,"uid":2419,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"做愛"},{"pid":"c1dc136556ff86b981659a53eae732e51fcaeeab","tid":554540,"uid":115510,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:26:33.000Z","msg":"修行, 婚姻生活, 生仔, 買樓, 大學學位, 升職加人工等等。。"},{"pid":"4004073e22a5cd63dde889277aef724b50cd87e0","tid":554540,"uid":138116,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:26:46.000Z","msg":"剪光頭"},{"pid":"10d6cbc06d57bf02272ac286b9b872db8fa994a6","tid":554540,"uid":126648,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:27:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱同呀爸呀媽傾計，佢哋覺得人要結婚，結完婚要生仔<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得最緊要開心同簡單就夠，如果覺得自己一個好開心既點解要結婚，冇能力又唔點中意小朋友既點解要生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同佢地傾呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上一輩都係洗左腦 幾窮都要結婚生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6569156ca7f4f141ce17c268ffc75bcb40472c71","tid":554540,"uid":97958,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"10d6cbc06d57bf02272ac286b9b872db8fa994a6","tid":554540,"uid":126648,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:27:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱同呀爸呀媽傾計，佢哋覺得人要結婚，結完婚要生仔<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得最緊要開心同簡單就夠，如果覺得自己一個好開心既點解要結婚，冇能力又唔點中意小朋友既點解要生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同佢地傾呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上一輩都係洗左腦 幾窮都要結婚生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇刻意傾，係咁啱傾開，佢地話咩親戚40幾歲都冇結婚又咩結左婚又唔生，但我聽到覺得一啲問題都冇"},{"pid":"53d72250ad5573c97f0477c073643a4033183cac","tid":554540,"uid":97958,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c1dc136556ff86b981659a53eae732e51fcaeeab","tid":554540,"uid":115510,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:26:33.000Z","msg":"修行, 婚姻生活, 生仔, 買樓, 大學學位, 升職加人工等等。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我呢啲爛泥睇到都覺得辛苦，我都想買樓，但我都唔信自己有咁既能力"},{"pid":"f5e9dd23a72e6591a38baa96559ef53a21efb725","tid":554540,"uid":74442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:34:49.000Z","msg":"屌屎眼"},{"pid":"bedf2e4350a93c506d060b6c4a2893122e0f967a","tid":554540,"uid":106430,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:44:28.000Z","msg":"偷情"},{"pid":"6f7ed119186ca30b1aece2e90965dafbe3f9da34","tid":554540,"uid":170998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"同幾個真心知己一齊去旅行<br />\n雖然通常因為工作忙好難搵到時間。。"},{"pid":"1637b90810ad122c29a9a9dcdc8ff776a3dd8729","tid":554540,"uid":115510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53d72250ad5573c97f0477c073643a4033183cac","tid":554540,"uid":97958,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c1dc136556ff86b981659a53eae732e51fcaeeab","tid":554540,"uid":115510,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:26:33.000Z","msg":"修行, 婚姻生活, 生仔, 買樓, 大學學位, 升職加人工等等。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T